89
00:08:04,276 --> 00:08:05,235
Ya, Bu.

90
00:08:05,402 --> 00:08:07,487
Ini. Ayo kembali bekerja.

91
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:13,118
Hei.

92
00:08:14,786 --> 00:08:16,163
Lihat mata Ibu.

93
00:08:16,371 --> 00:08:18,290
