Aku pencari gagasan...

220
00:17:45,732 --> 00:17:47,776
Bawa aku, gravitasi!

221
00:17:53,407 --> 00:17:55,075
Ini normal! Tetap berfokus!

222
00:17:59,413 --> 00:18:00,497
Jangan bergerak!

223
00:18:06,378 --> 00:18:07,921
